dc_description_s: These data layers represent roads and right of ways (ROW) for Grant County, Wisconsin in 2018. They are feature classes within the geodatabase Grant_Roads_ROW_2018.gdb. [Road centerlines for Grant County, Wisconsin. Digitized from Wisconsin aerial imagery and developed for emergency mapping.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For the most recent version of this data, please visit: http://www.grantcountylandrecords.com/publicinfo/
